character.name:
I want to recreate Kazuma from the anime Konosuba, so here is the description:
Hair: Medium brown (#7C543A), tousled and spiky, with several locks sticking out in different directions. The hair is parted slightly off-center and reaches just below the ears.
Cape: Deep teal green (#317773) with a golden yellow trim (#F6E27A). The cape is fastened around the neck with a black diamond-shaped clasp (#232323) and lays over the shoulders, draping to about mid-back. The inside of the cape is a muted gray (#888A8A).
Shirt: Off-white tunic (#F5F5F5) with long, light gray sleeves (#C2C2C2). The tunic has a black and silver ornamental design (#232323 and #C2C2C2) on the center chest.
Belt: Wide, dark brown belt (#5B3A29) with a square, muted gold buckle (#BFA76F).
Pants: Charcoal gray (#41424C), slim fitting and tucked into boots.
Boots: Tall, brown boots (#695040) reaching just below the knees, with slightly lighter brown cuffs (#A98A63) at the top.
Style: The character’s outfit is practical and classic fantasy adventurer style, with clean lines and solid color blocks suitable for pixel art. The overall silhouette is slim and slightly athletic.
